Class Protocol

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.client.io.Protocol
public class Protocol
extends Object

The methods in this class are used to modify the current system properties for the HTTP protocol.

Example:

    String tmpProp = props.getProperty(HTTP_PROXY_HOST);
    if(tmpProp != null){
          Protocol.setHttpProxyHost(tmpProp);
     }
